title: Fenton's Quest
creator: Mary Elizabeth Braddon
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Fenton's Quest, by Mary Elizabeth Braddon. This story revolves around Gilbert Fenton, a very talented middle class businessman from London, who falls in love with a beautiful country woman far below his station. He decides to marry her anyway. But is she all that she seems?
